<item>
            <title>[LU-4078] bad ERR_PTR() use in mdc_locks.c</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4078</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdc_intent_open_pack() returns NULL and ERR_PTR() while its caller mdc_enqueue() only checks its return value using IS_ERR(). mdc_intent_getattr_pack() returns ERR_PTRs but mdc_intent_getattr_async() checks its return value by comparing to NULL.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
